    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to brown, reduce the heat to medium, add the lid to the pan and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until the vegetables have softened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken & kimchi dak galbi</strong></p>",
