        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>chicken & kimchi dak galbi</strong> to a bowl and cover with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cooked rice</strong> to the pan and spread out with the back of a spoon</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until starting to crisp – this is your <strong>crispy rice</strong></p>",
